questions: How high is the share of people living in proximity of a busstop in Hoeri in the year 2010?
queries: SELECT T1.access_by_bus         FROM accessibility_bus AS T1         JOIN spatialunit AS T2 ON T1.spatialunit_id = T2.spatialunit_id         WHERE T2.name LIKE 'Hoeri' AND T1.year = 2010

questions: Which municipality has the highest share of people living in proximity of a busstop?
queries: SELECT T2.name         FROM spatialunit AS T2         JOIN accessibility_bus AS T1 ON T2.spatialunit_id = T1.spatialunit_id         ORDER BY T1.access_by_bus DESC LIMIT 1

questions: Which municipality has the minimum share of people living in proximity of a busstop?

questions: What are the highest, lowest and average share of people living in proximity of a busstop?
queries: SELECT MAX(T1.access_by_bus::numeric),         MIN(T1.access_by_bus::numeric), AVG(T1.access_by_bus::numeric)         FROM accessibility_bus AS T1

queries: SELECT T2.name         FROM total_registrations_electric_hybrid_cars AS T1         JOIN spatialunit AS T2 ON T1.spatialunit_id = T2.spatialunit_id         WHERE T2.type_id = 4 AND T1.year = 2005         ORDER BY T1.total_reg_electric_cars         LIMIT 1

questions: How high is the Total of electric and hybrid motor cars stock [%] in Truttikon in the year 2012?
queries: SELECT T1.total_electric_cars         FROM total_electric_hybrid_cars AS T1         JOIN spatialunit AS T2 ON T1.spatialunit_id = T2.spatialunit_id         WHERE T2.name LIKE 'Truttikon' AND T1.year = 2012

questions: Which municipality has the highest Total of electric and hybrid motor cars stock [%]?
queries: SELECT T2.name         FROM spatialunit AS T2         JOIN total_electric_hybrid_cars AS T1 ON T2.spatialunit_id = T1.spatialunit_id         ORDER BY T1.total_electric_cars DESC LIMIT 1

questions: Which municipality has the minimum Total of electric and hybrid motor cars stock [%]?
queries: SELECT T2.name         FROM spatialunit AS T2         JOIN total_electric_hybrid_cars AS T1 ON T2.spatialunit_id = T1.spatialunit_id         ORDER BY T1.total_electric_cars ASC LIMIT 1

questions: What are the highest, lowest and average Total of electric and hybrid motor cars stock [%]?
queries: SELECT MAX(T1.total_electric_cars::numeric),         MIN(T1.total_electric_cars::numeric), AVG(T1.total_electric_cars::numeric)         FROM total_electric_hybrid_cars AS T1

questions: How many municipalities have a Total of electric and hybrid motor cars stock [%] higher than 0.7 per year?
queries: SELECT T1.year, COUNT(*)         FROM total_electric_hybrid_cars AS T1         JOIN spatialunit AS T2 ON T1.spatialunit_id = T2.spatialunit_id         WHERE T1.total_electric_cars::numeric > 0.7 AND T2.type_id = 1         GROUP BY T1.year

questions: How high is the total Total of electric and hybrid motor cars stock [%] in the Canton Zurich in the year 2012?
queries: SELECT T1.total_electric_cars FROM total_electric_hybrid_cars AS T1         JOIN spatialunit AS T2 ON T1.spatialunit_id = T2.spatialunit_id         WHERE T2.type_id = 8 AND T1.year = 2012

questions: Which region had the lowest Total of electric and hybrid motor cars stock [%] in the year 2012?
queries: SELECT T2.name         FROM total_electric_hybrid_cars AS T1         JOIN spatialunit AS T2 ON T1.spatialunit_id = T2.spatialunit_id         WHERE T2.type_id = 4 AND T1.year = 2012         ORDER BY T1.total_electric_cars         LIMIT 1
